{"tid":2086694,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中聯辦聽日動員1000個街站撐立法喎","createTime":"2020-06-30T11:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T13:28:46.000Z","uid":238828,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c7676497b1f6467dc449587c9709d9701121e8ed","tid":2086694,"uid":238828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:24:36.000Z","msg":"『朱文(中聯辦協調部部長)⋯⋯呼籲他們動員支持「七一」全港一千個街站，支持立法⋯⋯多個建制社團、商會近日收到通知，明日「七一」要出席全港各區的撐國安立法街站，朱文在會上呼籲人大政協要踴躍出席。』<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/492371/泛民紛引退解散-中聯辦協調部長稱顯立法作用-明千個街站撐立法\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F492371%2F%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E7%B4%9B%E5%BC%95%E9%80%80%E8%A7%A3%E6%95%A3-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%8D%94%E8%AA%BF%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E7%A8%B1%E9%A1%AF%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8-%E6%98%8E%E5%8D%83%E5%80%8B%E8%A1%97%E7%AB%99%E6%92%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2Fw1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=30003161\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/492371/泛民紛引退解散-中聯辦協調部長稱顯立法作用-明千個街站撐立法</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廢老又有飯盒拎<br />\n點都好，聽日維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2df06ce8b5f3134fe9c3f14e869d487adf6a092","tid":2086694,"uid":42364,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:27:50.000Z","msg":"十八區721<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef486cde50416cfac8675ac0b2353b6d3db52ea2","tid":2086694,"uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"手足，大家聽日見，準備好道具比國際傳媒影啊<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Thanks, Pompeo</span></span></strong>比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2Fw1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=2a767467\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地、美國廢架制裁無用（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"f6142771ace7b558e6e3c16c4da43a3d5fddfb18","tid":2086694,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:30:30.000Z","msg":"分散狗力"},{"pid":"2f34357d96e3bf332b38ca5c6e64c18bea4f536e","tid":2086694,"uid":238828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:31:26.000Z","msg":"巧京京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日要去銅鑼灣撐下班廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b8897c4d22129d030dfb754968ac2ca6d7c6f3","tid":2086694,"uid":120627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:31:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>踴躍出席</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c15198f7ee79e71936f5c9eeaef9b2dabd3cf214","tid":2086694,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:31:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9ca7e51280a2ce6185217e7bf96743e47656828d","tid":2086694,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx0vodRn.png&amp;h=bffec503&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"1ef33a74f14c653f90241517a72531f836e460df","tid":2086694,"uid":52760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:32:18.000Z","msg":"聽日可能18區開花"},{"pid":"257dd3b0e31732162c477f21d786b9a335e99f97","tid":2086694,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:32:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">七一見</span>"},{"pid":"7de68ae0b92c8514b949fd3d01cd90a3ef061aa0","tid":2086694,"uid":173326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:33:34.000Z","msg":"藍絲掩護我地遊行"},{"pid":"254d8c56badc1659c293b6d420a45bd9835ced16","tid":2086694,"uid":27194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T11:36:11.000Z","msg":"立咗法啦 仲r支持<img 